section.about-canvs-section
  div.container
    div.row
      header.section-header-wrap
        h1.section-header Nuanced insights, completely automated.
      div.content-box.about-canvs-box.stop-counting
        img.about-canvs-illustration(src="images/stop-counting.svg")
        h2 Stop counting.<br>Start understanding.
        p You know how many people are talking about your show, but only Canvs can automatically tell you what they’re feeling. Spend your time building fascinating insights, not wading through Tweets.
      div.content-box.about-canvs-box.forget-sentiment
        img.about-canvs-illustration(src="images/forget-sentiment.svg")
        h2 Forget sentiment.<br>Discover meaning.
        p We know that social media sentiment tools suck because we’ve used them all. We don’t even believe in positive, negative, and neutral sentiment. Canvs uncovers nuanced audience emotions and lets you decide what they mean for your show.

    button.action-btn.request-demo-btn(data-toggle="modal", data-target=".contactModal") Request a Demo

