section.actionable-insights-section
  div.container
    div.row
      header.section-header-wrap
        h1.section-header Actionable insights for the TV ecosystem.
      div.content-box.actionable-insights-box
        div.icon-circle
          img.actionable-insights-illustration(src="images/marketing-icon.svg")
        h2 Marketing
        p You know how many people are talking about your show, but only Canvs can automatically tell you what they’re feeling. 
      div.content-box.actionable-insights-box
        div.icon-circle
          img.actionable-insights-illustration(src="images/adsales-icon.svg")
        h2 Ad Sales
        p Use Canvs to identify what other brands your most engaged audience loves. Then get to work selling super effective spots and integrations. 
      div.content-box.actionable-insights-box
        div.icon-circle
          img.actionable-insights-illustration(src="images/production-icon.svg")
        h2 Production
        p Use Canvs to get feedback in real time. Know immediately if that joke in the third act landed and if viewers hate the new villain as much as you want them to.

    button.action-btn.get-started-btn(data-toggle="modal", data-target=".contactModal") Get started with Canvs

